{"tid":736623,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"[JUPAS撚]呀媽誤會左我表哥入左HKU","createTime":"2018-07-10T11:10:09.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-10T13:10:35.000Z","uid":131369,"like":43,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"abc09daed4d19f467d7331f4041f981dcf1f42d1","tid":736623,"uid":131369,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-10T11:10:09.000Z","msg":"我表哥佢今年考dse，今日放榜<br />\n佢考得唔係太好，又怕呀媽擔心<br />\n呀媽一生人既夢想佢佢個仔入大學<br />\n因為佢d親戚街坊都無仔女入到U<br />\n<br />\n今日一早番左屋企時，呀媽係咁問佢成績點，夠唔夠分, 可以入邊間U<br />\n表哥心情唔好，是撚但但同呀媽佢佢去讀藥劑，<br />\n之後請入房訓較(尋晚通左頂)<br />\n<br />\n表哥起左身，屙完屎之後出黎<br />\n發現成家人都好開心，呀爸呀媽叫撚晒佢d親戚姑嫂話今晚出黎食飯<br />\n同個仔慶祝入到HKU讀藥劑<br />\n<br />\n依個時候先知大撚獲<br />\n表哥其實係去報IVE讀藥劑<br />\n唔撚知邊個親戚街坊話係香港既大學，只有HKU有藥劑讀<br />\n所以呀媽以為佢夠分入左HKU<br />\n<br />\n屌你<br />\n我表哥頭先打電話比我<br />\n問我點做好.........<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 點算好"},{"pid":"48a0f15cc000aab721df9c6e3217f0e839803188","tid":736623,"uid":21423,"like":10,"dislike":1,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-10T11:13:14.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"fcdb3e383e8a63d894d676c78b88b079252c9829","tid":736623,"uid":4876,"like":23,"dislike":1,"score":22,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-10T11:13:47.000Z","msg":"早左啦柒頭"},{"pid":"a29e7a1a11bff210527a4c79c4216ca3ae5267e0","tid":736623,"uid":179571,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-10T11:15:21.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"3dce4af8265b23424739788baa1a2813ce7a7172","tid":736623,"uid":146917,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-10T11:15:28.000Z","msg":"未來人？"},{"pid":"aacda913c2c795eef390032e4326e9b067b7fde4","tid":736623,"uid":176910,"like":25,"dislike":0,"score":25,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-10T11:16:14.000Z","msg":"你早咗12個鐘，聽日再post過啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" c